T02TD3245BE:12a-1: a'arya dz'am gu l'i s'a dha nam /
T02TD3245BE:12a-3: 'phags ma dug sel ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3245BE:12a-4: sngar bshad pa'i cho ga'i rim pas stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes thogs la /
T02TD3245BE:12a-5: padma dmar po dang zla ba la yi ge dz'am ser po yongs su gyur pas 'phags ma dug sel ma ser mo zhal gsum phyag drug mar skad cig gis rdzogs par bya ste /
T02TD3245BE:12a-6: g-yas pa dang cig shos kyi zhal ni mthing nag dang dkar po //
T02TD3245BE:12a-7: ral gri dang rdo rje dang mda' ni g-yas pa'i phyag gsum na'o //
T02TD3245BE:12a-8: sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhags pa dang /
T02TD3245BE:12a-9: dug gi me tog dang gzhu ni g-yon gyi gsum na'o //
T02TD3245BE:12a-10: gdengs ka rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor dbus la gnas pa /
T02TD3245BE:12a-11: sbrul dang lha rdzas kyi na bza' dang /
T02TD3245BE:12a-13: gzhon nu ma'i mtshan rnams kyis mchog tu 'bar ba /
T02TD3245BE:12a-14: dbu la mi bskyod pa bzhugs par bsgoms la sngags bzla bar bya ste /
T02TD3245BE:12a-15: aom dz'am gu l'i sarba bi sha pra sha ma ni phu sv'a h'a /
T02TD3245BE:12a-16: 'phags ma dug sel ma'i sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3245BE:12a-18: // / byang chub sems dpa'i zhal snga nas dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
